e="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>p</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordm; 44&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 20&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>q</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordm; 44&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 21&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>r</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordm; 47&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 21&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>06/11/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>06/11/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>06/11/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>19/07/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>05/06/2026</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 19/7/2004 sino alla pronuncia di compatibilit&agrave; ambientale e d&apos;intesa della Regione Basilicata (DM 8/10/2004). Con DM 19/12/2025 di ripristino del permesso per annullamento PiTESAI il termine della sospensione &egrave; stato determinato al 5/6/2026.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>7.991 (7987 trascorsi)</td></tr></table>Attualmente sospeso (4 giorni di sospensione restanti).<br>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 7.987 giorni (circa&nbsp;21&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;11&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/11/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_19981106.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/11/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/08/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/04/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIII N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/03/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Cambio intestazione quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/03/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Rettifica</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/11/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/10/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_20001011.pdf" target=_blank>Nomina r.u.</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">15/09/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/11/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_20001129.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/03/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/04/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Cambio intestazione quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/05/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Assunzione quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/02/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/03/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Assunzione quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/02/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVII N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/07/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Cambio intestazione quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/05/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVII N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">08/10/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Sospensione decorso temporale</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/07/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVIII N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/02/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_20100209.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LIV N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/03/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_20220329.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/08/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/09/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_20220929.pdf" target=_blank>Revoca</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/09/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/11/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/492_20251119.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/11/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4p