  <Placemark>
      <name>BELGIOIOSO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Permesso di Ricerca</h3><h2>BELGIOIOSO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>2107</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/11/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>322,00 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>Presentata istanza di autorizzazione alla perforazione del pozzo esplorativo &laquo;BELLA 1&raquo; pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LVI - N. 9.<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ALEANNA ITALIA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>LOMBARDIA (318,35 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Pavia (210,07 km<sup>2</sup>)<br>Lodi (91,93 km<sup>2</sup>)<br>Milano (16,35 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr><tr><td valign=top>EMILIA-ROMAGNA (3,66 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Piacenza (3,66 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 08&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 16&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 16&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 12&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 52&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 12&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 52&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 07&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 59&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 07&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 59&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 06&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 06&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>i</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 05&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>l</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 04&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 05&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>m</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 04&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 06&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>n</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 06&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 06&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>o</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 06&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 07&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>p</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 10&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 07&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>q</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 10&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 08&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>r</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 12&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 08&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>s</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 12&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 10&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>t</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 08&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 10&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>22/11/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>22/11/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>22/11/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 7 settembre 2017, istanza di proroga con riduzione pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXI - N. 9<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>12/02/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>30/11/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>291</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>13/02/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>01/10/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Decreto-legge 14 dicembre 2018, n.135, art. 11-ter, commi 6-8, convertito con modificazioni dalla Legge 11 febbraio 2019 n. 12 (Moratoria del Piano per la transizione energetica sostenibile delle aree idonee - PiTESAI).</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>961</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>11/02/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>29/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospensione disposta dal decreto 28/04/2025 di ripristino e sospensione del decorso temporale.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.173</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 2.425 giorni (circa&nbsp;6&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;8&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/11/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20101122.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/11/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LIV N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/06/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20130620.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/02/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVII N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/01/2014</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20140117.pdf" target=_blank>Termine della sospensione del decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/11/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVIII N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/07/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20220722.pdf" target=_blank>Revoca parziale e riperimetrazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/07/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/04/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20230406.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/02/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVII N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20250428.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino dell&apos;area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20250428.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2107_20250428.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/02/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 4</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
