  <Placemark>
      <name>CALCIO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Permesso di Ricerca</h3><h2>CALCIO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>2113</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/03/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>154,60 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>Presentata istanza di autorizzazione alla perforazione del pozzo esplorativo &laquo;FONTANELLA 1&raquo; pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LX - N. 12.<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">PENGAS ITALIANA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>LOMBARDIA (154,6 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Bergamo (86,63 km<sup>2</sup>)<br>Cremona (67,97 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 50&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 32&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 46&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 32&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 46&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 30&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 40&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 30&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 40&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 36&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 36&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 22&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 42&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 22&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>i</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 42&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>l</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 50&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/03/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/03/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/03/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 13 luglio 2022, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXVI - N. 7<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>05/09/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 5/9/2024 e fino alla data di adozione del provvedimento conclusivo (espresso o di diniego) relativo all'istanza di autorizzazione preventiva al trasferimento della titolarit&agrave;.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>635</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>31/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>30/06/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 31/12/2016 fino al rilascio dell'intesa regionale e comunque per un periodo non superiore a 18 mesi.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>546</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>30/06/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>31/12/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 30/06/2018 fino al rilascio dell&apos;intesa regionale e autorizzazione alla perforazione del pozzo FONTANELLA 1 e comunque per un periodo non superiore a mesi 18.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>549</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>13/02/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>01/10/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Decreto-legge 14 dicembre 2018, n.135, art. 11-ter, commi 6-8, convertito con modificazioni dalla Legge 11 febbraio 2019 n. 12 (Moratoria del Piano per la transizione energetica sostenibile delle aree idonee - PiTESAI).</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>961</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 2.691 giorni (circa&nbsp;7&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;5&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/03/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2113_20110307.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/03/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LV N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">15/12/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2113_20171215.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXI N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/11/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2113_20181105.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/06/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/07/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2113_20220722.pdf" target=_blank>Conferma dell&apos;area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/07/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/03/2026</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2113_20260326.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/09/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXX N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/03/2026</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2113_20260326.pdf" target=_blank>Riduzione area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/03/2026</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXX N. 3</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
