style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/09/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/525_20220929.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/03/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/525_20240328.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVIII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/525_20250417.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino dell&apos;area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/04/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 4</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
