  <Placemark>
      <name>SANTA CROCE</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Permesso di Ricerca</h3><h2>SANTA CROCE</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>2110</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/12/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>745,60 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>Presentata istanza di differimento della data di inizio perforazione del pozzo esplorativo pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LIX - N. 1.<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">IRMINIO</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>MOLISE (641,2 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Campobasso (641,2 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr><tr><td valign=top>CAMPANIA (104,4 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Benevento (104,4 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 04&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 37&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 24&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 37&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 24&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 19&apos;,84</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 19&apos;,34</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 21&apos;,67</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 17&apos;,5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 21&apos;,9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 17&apos;,48</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 21&apos;,8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 17&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 21&apos;,86</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>i</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 17&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 21&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>l</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 09&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 21&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>m</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 09&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>n</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 04&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>16/12/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>16/12/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>16/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 16 maggio 2016, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LX - N. 5<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>26/03/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>26/09/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 26/3/2016 fino a pronuncia del Ministero dell&apos;Ambiente su valutazione di impatto ambientale per l'esecuzione del RILIEVO GEOFISICO 3D SANTA CROCE e comunque per un periodo non superiore a 18 mesi.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>549</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>26/09/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>11/06/2026</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 26/9/2017 fino a conclusione procedura di valutazione impatto ambientale per il progetto  RILIEVO GEOFISICO 3D SANTA CROCE e comunque fino ad un termine massimo di dodici mesi dal 11/6/2025, data del decreto di ripristino.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>3.180 (3170 trascorsi)</td></tr></table>Attualmente sospeso (10 giorni di sospensione restanti).<br>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 3.719 giorni (circa&nbsp;10&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;2&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/12/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2110_20101216.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/12/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LV N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">18/09/2014</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2110_20140918.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/12/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVIII N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/05/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2110_20170502.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/03/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXI N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/10/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2110_20221031.pdf" target=_blank>Revoca</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/10/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/06/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2110_20250611.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/06/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 6</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
