2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>23/02/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>23/02/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>05/11/2007</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 5/11/2007 (data parere favorevole VIA della regione) sino alla data di rilascio intesa da parte della Regione Basilicata. 
Con successivo decreto sar&agrave; determinato il termine finale della sospensione.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>6.784</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>11/07/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>22/05/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.776</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>30/04/2007</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>05/11/2007</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>189</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 8.749 giorni (circa&nbsp;24&nbsp;anni)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/07/1994</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/410_19940711.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/07/1994</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVIII N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/03/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/410_19950306.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/01/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXIX N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/06/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/410_19960614.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota e nomina r.u.</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/06/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/410_19960614.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/01/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/12/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/410_19961205.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/10/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLI N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/08/1997</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/410_19970828.pdf" target=_blank>Tr