d style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 39&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>z</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 02&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 38&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 01&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 38&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 01&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 39&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 39&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 40&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>0&ordm; 56&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 40&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>21/09/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>21/09/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>21/09/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 21 dicembre 2007, istanza di proroga con riduzione pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LII - N. 1<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>11/08/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dall&apos; 11/8/2008 sino alla pronuncia dell&apos;intesa da parte della Regione Abruzzo. 
Con successivo decreto sar&agrave; determinato il termine finale della sospensione.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>6.504</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>29/05/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>10/09/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.200</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 7.704 giorni (circa&nbsp;21&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;1&nbsp;mese)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">21/09/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_19980921.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">21/09/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/02/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_19990210.pdf" target=_blank>Assunzione quote e nomina r.u.</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">21/02/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/03/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20000320.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/05/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20000529.pdf" target=_blank>Approvazione programma lavori unitario</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/05/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/04/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20010420.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/01/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20030127.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/06/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVII N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">08/10/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20031008.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/05/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVII N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">04/10/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20061004.pdf" target=_blank>Determinazione scadenza vigenza</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/09/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno L N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/01/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20100128.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/08/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LIV N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/10/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20221031.pdf" target=_blank>Revoca</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/10/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVI N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">08/05/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/484_20250508.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">08/05/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 5</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
