ft>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>16/04/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>16/04/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>03/12/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 3/12/1999 sino agli accordi di programma previsti dal Decreto VIA del Ministero dell&apos;ambiente n 4507 del 03/12/1999.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>9.678</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>01/04/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>03/12/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.707</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 11.385 giorni (circa&nbsp;31&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;2&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style