 grey;" valign=top>01/12/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>03/12/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.463</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 11.141 giorni (circa&nbsp;30&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;6&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/12/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_19951201.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/12/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/02/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_19980213.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/02/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_19990211.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/12/1995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/03/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_20020314.pdf" target=_blank>Determinazione scadenza sospensione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/03/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVI N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/03/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_20020314.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/12/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVI N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_20231229.pdf" target=_blank>Revoca</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVII N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/12/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/625_20251212.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"