ign=center>17&ordm; 38&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 18&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>15/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>15/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>15/12/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>18/02/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>04/01/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dal 18/02/2017 fino al 04/01/2019, data dell&apos;ultima sentenza definitiva di pronuncia in merito ai ricorsi presentati al TAR Lazio dalla Regione Calabria e dai Comuni di Crosia, Crotone, Rossano e Villapiana.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>685</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>13/02/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>01/10/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Decreto-legge 14 dicembre 2018, n.135, art. 11-ter, commi 6-8, convertito con modificazioni dalla Legge 11 febbraio 2019 n. 12 (Moratoria del Piano per la transizione energetica sostenibile delle aree idonee - PiTESAI).</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>961</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>11/02/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>18/12/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dall'11 febbraio 2022 al 17 dicembre 2025, data del decreto di ripristino dell&apos;area di ricerca.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.406</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 3.052 giorni (circa&nbsp;8&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;4&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">15/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2135_20161215.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">15/12/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LX N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2135_20171229.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">18/02/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/12/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2135_20251217.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino dell&apos;area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/02/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/12/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2135_20251217.pdf" target=_blank>Sospensione decorso temporale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/02/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 12</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
