2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/12/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>SOSPENSIONI DEL DECORSO TEMPORALE</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left>Giorni&nbsp;di&nbsp;sospensione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>13/02/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>01/10/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Decreto-legge 14 dicembre 2018, n.135, art. 11-ter, commi 6-8, convertito con modificazioni dalla Legge 11 febbraio 2019 n. 12 (Moratoria del Piano per la transizione energetica sostenibile delle aree idonee - PiTESAI).</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>961</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>11/02/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>20/12/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=left valign=top>Sospeso dall'11 febbraio 2022 al 19 dicembre 2025, data del decreto di ripristino dell&apos;area di ricerca.</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right valign=top>1.408</td></tr></table>Il permesso &egrave; stato sospeso per un totale di 2.369 giorni (circa&nbsp;6&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;6&nbsp;mesi)<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/12/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2138_20181207.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/12/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2138_20231229.pdf" target=_blank>Revoca parziale e riperimetrazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVII N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/12/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2138_20251219.pdf" target=_blank>Ripristino dell&apos;area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/12/2023</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIX N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid gre