1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>10/07/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>10/07/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>10/07/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 8 gennaio 2018, istanza di proroga con riduzione pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXII - N. 1<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/07/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/2003_20120710.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/07/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVI N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/07/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><