  <Placemark>
      <name>COLLE DI LAURO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>COLLE DI LAURO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>790</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/10/1972</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/09/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>33,62 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 19.593 giorni (circa&nbsp;53&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;8&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>62,42%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">GAS PLUS ITALIANA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>25,08%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>12,5%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>MOLISE (33,62 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Campobasso (33,62 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 28&apos;,17</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 54&apos;,29</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 28&apos;,49</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 53&apos;,69</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 29&apos;,88</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 54&apos;,09</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 31&apos;,67</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 50&apos;,64</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 28&apos;,72</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 49&apos;,78</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 26&apos;,93</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 53&apos;,24</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 26&apos;,42</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 53&apos;,09</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 26&apos;,12</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 53&apos;,7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>i</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 28&apos;,17</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 54&apos;,29</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>09/10/1972</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Unificazione</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>09/10/1972</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/1994</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>22</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>La concessione COLLE DI LAURO deriva dall&apos;unificazione di 3 preesistenti concessioni.</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/08/1985</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/1994</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>10</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>2&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>10/12/2009</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/2009</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/2014</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>3&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>06/12/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/2014</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/09/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 19 settembre 2017, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXI - N. 9<br>Presentata, in data 13 settembre 2022, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXVI - N. 9<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><t