  <Placemark>
      <name>LIPPONE-MAZARA</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>LIPPONE-MAZARA</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>327</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/12/1960</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>6&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/10/2027</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>16,57 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI MEDITERRANEA IDROCARBURI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>SICILIA (16,57 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trapani (16,57 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 38&apos;,58</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>37&ordm; 45&apos;,28</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 39&apos;,97</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>37&ordm; 45&apos;,65</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 42&apos;,03</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>37&ordm; 45&apos;,68</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 43&apos;,57</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>37&ordm; 45&apos;,68</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 44&apos;,3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>37&ordm; 44&apos;,68</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 39&apos;,6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>37&ordm; 44&apos;,07</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>22/12/1960</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>25/02/1961</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>25/02/1981</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>30</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento della concessione LIPPONE. La concessione &egrave; stata conferita per 20 anni dalla data del 25/02/1961 ma con successivo provvedimento di unificazione del 19/2/1981 la durata &egrave; stata modificata in 30 anni fino al 21/2/1991.</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>19/05/1962</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/10/1962</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/10/1982</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>30</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento della concessione MAZARA DEL VALLO. La concessione &egrave; stata conferita per 20 anni dalla data del 13/10/1962 ma con successivo provvedimento di unificazione del 19/2/1981 la durata &egrave; stata modificata in 30 anni fino al 13/10/1992.</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>19/02/1981</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Unificazione</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>19/02/1981</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/10/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>30</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Unificazione delle concessioni LIPPONE e MAZARA DEL VALLO. La scadenza della concessione unificata &egrave; fissata al 13/10/1992, data di scadenza dell&apos;originaria concessione MAZARA DEL VALLO.</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordf;&nbs