      <name>MAFALDA</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>MAFALDA</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>828</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/12/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/12/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>43,42 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 12 gennaio 2021, istanza di variazione del programma dei lavori pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXV - N. 1<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 15.155 giorni (circa&nbsp;41&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;6&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">GAS PLUS ITALIANA(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>60%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>40%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>MOLISE (43,42 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Campobasso (43,42 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 19&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 21&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 21&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 57&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 23&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 57&apos;</td></