 1px solid grey;">11/01/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/819_20180111.pdf" target=_blank>Approvazione nuovo programma lavori</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/01/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/01/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/819_20180111.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga e riperimetrazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/02/2014</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/07/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/819_20190730.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/02/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXIII N. 7</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Centrali di raccolta e trattamento</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi in produzione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 009</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 015 DIR A</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 016</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 020 DIR B</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi produttivi non eroganti</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 004</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 005 DIR A</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 007</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 008</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 010</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>6</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 011</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>7</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 013</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>8</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 014</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>9</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 017 DIR A</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>10</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 018</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>11</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 021</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 022</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 024 DIR A</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TORRENTE TONA 025 DIR</td></tr></table></div><br>]]></description>
