  <Placemark>
      <name>MIGLIANICO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>MIGLIANICO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>930</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/04/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/04/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>16,60 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 8.809 giorni (circa&nbsp;24&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;2&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>ABRUZZO (16,6 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Chieti (16,6 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 51&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra il parallelo 42&ordm;24&apos; e la linea di costa a bassa marea</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra la linea di costa a bassa marea ed il meridiano 1&ordm;54&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 54&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 22&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 50&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 22&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 50&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 23&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 51&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 23&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>19/04/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>19/04/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>19/04/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>20</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 16 aprile 2020, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXIV - N. 4<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/04/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/04/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVI N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/07/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Modifica programma lavori</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">06/07/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIX N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/02/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/930_20100209.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LIV N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">21/11/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/930_20161121.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LX N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/03/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/930_20210301.pdf" target=_blank>Accettazione rinuncia parziale e riduzione area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/03/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXV N. 3</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi produttivi non eroganti</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">MIGLIANICO 001</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">MIGLIANICO 002 DIR A</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi non produttivi</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">GRANCIARO 001</td></tr></table></div><br>]]></description>
