  <Placemark>
      <name>MISANO ADRIATICO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>MISANO ADRIATICO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>858</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/06/1990</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/06/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>2,48 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 13.130 giorni (circa&nbsp;36&nbsp;anni).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">CANOEL ITALIA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>EMILIA-ROMAGNA (2,44 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Rimini (2,44 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr><tr><td valign=top>MARCHE (0,04 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Pesaro e Urbino (0,04 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>0&ordm; 12&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>0&ordm; 13&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>0&ordm; 13&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 57&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>0&ordm; 12&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 57&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>20/06/1990</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>20/06/1990</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>20/06/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>30</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 14 giugno 2018, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXII - N. 6<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/06/1990</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_19900620.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/06/1990</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXV N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/05/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_19960509.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/03/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/06/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_19960614.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/01/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/06/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_19960614.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota e nomina r.u.</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/02/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_20010207.pdf" target=_blank>Nomina r.u.</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">18/10/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/02/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_20010207.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">18/10/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/02/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_20010207.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/02/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/04/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/11/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVI N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/06/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/03/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVII N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/11/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/09/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVII N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/03/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento quota</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/12/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIX N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/06/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/04/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIX N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/04/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_20080416.pdf" target=_blank>Intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/02/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LII N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/06/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_20130628.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/06/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVII N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/12/2019</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/858_20191220.pdf" target=_blank>Accettaz