style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/01/1962</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/749_19620122.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/01/1962</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno VI N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/04/1971</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/749_19710403.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">03/04/1971</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XV N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/12/1985</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/749_19851216.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/12/1985</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXX N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/09/1993</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/749_19930909.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/01/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVII N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/11/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/01/2002</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVIII N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/04/2007</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Trasferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/11/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LI N. 5</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Centrali di raccolta e trattamento</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">PONTEPARMA</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi in produzione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">POGGIO CASTIONE 002</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">POGGIO CASTIONE 004</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">POGGIO CASTIONE 005</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">POGGIO CASTIONE 006</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 