  <Placemark>
      <name>RAPAGNANO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>RAPAGNANO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>938</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/11/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/11/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>8,49 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>La concessione deriva dalla riattribuzione ad altro operatore della originaria Concessione di coltivazione RAPAGNANO (Eni 100%) vigente dal 17/04/1960 al 28/11/2012.<br>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 4.933 giorni (circa&nbsp;13&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;6&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">APENNINE ENERGY</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>MARCHE (8,49 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Ascoli Piceno (8,49 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 08&apos;,92</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 09&apos;,98</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 11&apos;,05</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 08&apos;,29</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 09&apos;,97</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 07&apos;,56</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 07&apos;,84</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 09&apos;,25</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/11/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Riattribuzione</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/11/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/11/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>10</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 9 novembre 2021, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXV - N. 11<br>Presentata, in data 31 ottobre 2025, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXIX - N. 10<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/11/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/938_20121128.pdf" target=_blank>Riattribuzione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/11/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVI N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/04/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/938_20130417.pdf" target=_blank>Modifica denominazione sociale</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/12/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVII N. 4</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Centrali di raccolta e trattamento</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">RAPAGNANO</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi in produzione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">RAPAGNANO 001</td></tr></table></div><br>]]></description>
