      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>SALGASTRI</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>707</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/10/1938</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/10/2013</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>11,45 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 31.997 giorni (circa&nbsp;87&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;8&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">LAZZI GAS</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>EMILIA-ROMAGNA (11,45 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="p