  <Placemark>
      <name>SALSOMAGGIORE I</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>SALSOMAGGIORE I</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>726</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">11/07/1897</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>perpetua</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>4,37 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>Perpetua.<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 47.076 giorni (circa&nbsp;129&nbsp;anni).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SOCIET&Agrave; DI SALSOMAGGIORE S.R.L. IN LIQUIDAZIONE</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>EMILIA-ROMAGNA (4,37 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Parma (4,37 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 29&apos;,17</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 49&apos;,58</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 28&apos;,4</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 49&apos;,58</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 28&apos;,3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 49&apos;,42</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 27&apos;,28</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 49&apos;,12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-2&ordm; 27&apos;,28</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px soli