      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>SAN MARCO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>862</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/07/1991</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/07/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>40,09 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 12.746 giorni (circa&nbsp;34&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;11&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>MARCHE (40,09 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Fermo (39,79 km<sup>2</sup>)<br>Ascoli Piceno (0,3 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 15&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 13&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 19&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 13&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 19&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 12&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 20&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 12&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: