  <Placemark>
      <name>SETTALA</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>SETTALA</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>913</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1997</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>33,75 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 10.743 giorni (circa&nbsp;29&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;5&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SOCIET&Agrave; PADANA ENERGIA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>LOMBARDIA (33,75 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Milano (26,43 km<sup>2</sup>)<br>Lodi (7,32 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 05&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 01&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 01&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 26&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 02&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 26&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>-3&ordm; 02&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=ce