erimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/03/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVII N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/05/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/850_19960509.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/03/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/05/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/850_19960509.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/02/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/850_20040209.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/10/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVIII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/10/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/850_20081020.pdf" target=_blank>Riattribuzione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/10/2008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LII N. 11</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Centrali di raccolta e trattamento</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">MONTENEVOSO</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi in produzione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">MONTENEVOSO 001 DIR</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">TOMBOLO 002 DIR</td></tr></table></div><br>]]></description>
