      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>A.C 11.AG</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>981</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/10/1979</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/10/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>84,67 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 17.023 giorni (circa&nbsp;46&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;8&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA A (84,67 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra il meridiano 13&ordm;21&apos; e la linea di delimitazione Italia-Croazia</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra il meridiano 13&ordm;33&apos; e la linea di delimitazione Italia-Croazia</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 33&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 13&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 31&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 13&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 31&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 14&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="p