  <Placemark>
      <name>A.C 16.AG</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>A.C 16.AG</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>995</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/05/1985</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/05/2015</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>539,84 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Concessione in alto Adriatico, la produzione &egrave; sospesa ai sensi dell&apos;art. 8 del Decreto Legge 25 giugno 2008, n.  112 in attesa dell'accertamento, da parte del Ministero dell'Ambiente - ISPRA, sulla base di specifici studi in corso, dell&apos;assenza di rischi di subsidenza sulle coste.<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 14.988 giorni (circa&nbsp;41&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;1&nbsp;mese).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA A (539,84 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 46&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 13&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra il parallelo 45&ordm;13&apos; e la linea di delimitazione Italia - Croazia</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra la linea di delimitazione Italia-Croazia ed il parallelo 44&ordm;58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 51&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 51&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 59&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 48&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 59&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 48&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 00&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 49&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 00&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>i</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 49&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 01&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>l</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 51&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 01&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>m</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 51&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>45&ordm; 02&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>n</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&o