arget=_blank>Attribuzione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1997</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/04/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1014_20120405.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVI N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/12/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1014_20241230.pdf" target=_blank>Accettazione rinuncia parziale e riduzione area</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/12/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXVIII N. 12</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Piattaforme marine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ANGELA ANGELINA</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ANGELA CLUSTER</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid gre