  <Placemark>
      <name>B.C  1.LF</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>B.C  1.LF</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>954</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/08/1970</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/08/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>45,95 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 20.367 giorni (circa&nbsp;55&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;10&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>95%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">GAS PLUS ITALIANA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>5%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA B (45,95 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 34&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 15&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 40&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 15&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 40&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 14&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 41&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 14&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 41&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 12&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra il parallelo 42&ordm;12&apos; e la linea di costa a bassa marea</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra la linea di costa a bassa marea ed il meridiano 14&ordm;34&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/1970</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/1970</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>30</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>31/05/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2000</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>10</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>2&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>16/04/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2010</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2015</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>3&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/09/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2015</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>4&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/02/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>27/08/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 9 agosto 2023, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXVII - N. 8<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/08/1970</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_19700827.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/08/1970</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XV N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/09/1974</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_19740902.pdf" target=_blank>Ampliamento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/05/1974</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XIX N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/04/1979</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_19790419.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/11/1978</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXIII N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">04/08/1993</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_19930804.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/04/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVII N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/05/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_19960509.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/05/1996</td><td 