0160907.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga e riperimetrazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/08/2015</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LX N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/08/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_20180801.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/07/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/02/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_20210213.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">27/08/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXV N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/03/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/954_20210319.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/02/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXV N. 3</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Piattaforme marine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE 101</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE 1-9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE 3-7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE 8 BIS</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Centrali di raccolta e trattamento</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi in produzione</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">SANTO STEFANO MARE 009 DIR</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Pozzi produttivi non eroganti</th></tr><tr><td style="pad