      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>B.C  8.LF</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>971</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/03/1978</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">09/03/2028</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>262,00 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 17.616 giorni (circa&nbsp;48&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;3&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>61,7175%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>38,2825%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA B (262 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 52&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 18&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 58&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 18&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 58&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 17&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 59&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>42&ordm; 17&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 59&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" 