  <Placemark>
      <name>C.C  6.EO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>C.C  6.EO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>991</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/02/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/12/2027</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>63,46 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 15.445 giorni (circa&nbsp;42&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;4&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>60%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>40%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA C (63,46 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 32&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 36&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 34&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 36&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 34&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 35&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 35&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 35&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 35&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=cen