 32&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>o</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 33&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 33&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>p</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>14&ordm; 32&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 33&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>17/02/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento e unificazione</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>17/02/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/12/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>28</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>La scadenza corrisponde a quella dell&apos;originaria concessione C.C 5.ME con la quale la concessione C.C 6.EO &egrave; stata conferita e unificata.</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/11/2015</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/12/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/12/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>10</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>2&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>14/06/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/12/2022</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>28/12/2027</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 17 dicembre 2025, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXIX - N. 12<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/02/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19840217.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento e unificazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">17/02/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXVIII N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/10/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19841010.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/10/1984</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXIX N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/08/1985</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19850807.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1985</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXIX N. 12</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/07/1990</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19900702.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/07/1989</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXV N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/05/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19920512.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/06/1991</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVI N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/01/1993</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19930102.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">16/01/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVII N. 9</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/09/1993</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19930902.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">15/10/1992</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVII N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/02/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19980213.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">29/09/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19990929.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">30/11/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIII N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">10/12/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_19991210.pdf" target=_blank>Assunzione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/12/1999</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLIV N. 1</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/02/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_20040212.pdf" target=_blank>Intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/12/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVIII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/11/2015</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_20151113.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">28/12/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LIX N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/08/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/991_20180801.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/07/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 7</td></