padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 26 marzo 2024, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXVIII - N. 3<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/09/1982</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/983_19820913.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/03/1981</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXVI N. 10</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/07/1994</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/983_19940705.pdf" target=_blank>Aggiornamento programma lavori</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/07/1994</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXXVIII N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/02/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/983_19980213.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 