  <Placemark>
      <name>G.C  1.AG</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>G.C  1.AG</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>1026</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/10/2014</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">31/10/2034</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>145,60 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 4.231 giorni (circa&nbsp;11&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;7&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI MEDITERRANEA IDROCARBURI(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>60%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>40%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA G (145,6 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 42&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 59&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 44&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 59&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 44&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 48&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>36&ordm; 58&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>13&ordm; 48&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 