  <Placemark>
      <name>PORTO CORSINI MARE</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>PORTO CORSINI MARE</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>1008</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">14/09/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>107,70 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>La concessione deriva dall&apos;unificazione delle preesistenti concessioni &laquo;PORTO CORSINI MARE&raquo; e &laquo;FASCIA PORTO CORSINI MARE&raquo;, dalla successiva unificazione con la porzione sud, comprendente il giacimento PORTO CORSINI MARE EST, della preesistente concessione &laquo;A.C1.AG&raquo; e dall'ampliamento sulle porzioni di area in cui insiste parte del campo PORTO CORSINI MARE EST rilasciate dalle confinanti concessioni &laquo;A.C29.EA&raquo; e &laquo;A.C30.EA&raquo;<br>Fino al completamento delle procedure autorizzative in corso, la concessione produce ai sensi del Decreto Legge 18 ottobre 2012, n. 179 (art. 34, comma 19).<br>Il titolo &egrave; vigente da 10.835 giorni (circa&nbsp;29&nbsp;anni&nbsp;e&nbsp;8&nbsp;mesi).<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENI</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>ZONE MARINE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top colspan=2>ZONA A (107,7 km<sup>2</sup>)</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 29&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 27&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 34&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 27&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 34&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 25&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 36&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 25&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 36&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 38&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 38&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 20&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra la linea di delimitazione della ex zona ENI ed il parallelo 44&ordm;20&apos;,</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>i</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2 align=center>Intersezione tra la linea di delimitazione della ex zona ENI ed il parallelo 44&ordm;24&apos;,</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>l</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>12&ordm; 29&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>44&ordm; 24&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>05/10/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Unificazione</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>01/10/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>10</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>La concessione PORTO CORSINI MARE deriva dall&apos;unificazione delle preesistenti concessioni PORTO CORSINI MARE e FASCIA PORTO CORSINI MARE .</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>07/07/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>2&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/03/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>3&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>13/04/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>26/05/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>4&ordf;&nbsp;proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>23/12/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga e unificazione</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>23/12/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>14/09/2025</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>5</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Proroga e unificazione della concessione &laquo;PORTO CORSINI MARE&raquo; e della porzione sud, comprendente il giacimento PORTO CORSINI MARE EST, della concessione &laquo;A.C1.AG&raquo;</td></tr></table>Presentata, in data 14 settembre 2023, istanza di proroga pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXVII - N. 9<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">05/10/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1008_19961005.pdf" target=_blank>Unificazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/10/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/02/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1008_19980213.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">04/07/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1008_20010704.pdf" target=_blank>Approvazione nuovo programma di sviluppo e ricerca</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">04/07/2001</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLV N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">07/07/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1008_20060707.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/05/2006</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno L N. 8</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/03/2012</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1008_20120313.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/05/2011</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LVI N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/04/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1008_20170413.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/05/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXI N. 4</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/12/2020</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px;