o XLII N. 6</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">21/11/2016</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1015_20161121.pdf" target=_blank>Proroga e riduzione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/2017</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LX N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/04/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1015_20210423.pdf" target=_blank>Accettazione rinuncia</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/04/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXV N. 4</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Piattaforme marine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">MORENA 1</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" colspan=2>Centrali di raccolta e trattamento</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">RUBICONE</td></tr></table></div><br><div style=&apos;float:left; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px;&apos;><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px soli