  <Placemark>
      <name>MASSERIA ACQUASALSA</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>MASSERIA ACQUASALSA</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>798</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/01/1975</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/01/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>41,22 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table>Sono in corso le procedure di verifica dell'avvenuta realizzazione delle attivit&agrave; di ripristino ambientale ai fini dell'accettazione dell'istanza di rinuncia.<br>Presentata, in data 22 gennaio 2018, istanza di rinuncia pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LXII - N. 1<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">GAS PLUS ITALIANA(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>46,03%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>45,17%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">CANOEL ITALIA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>8,8%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>PUGLIA (41,22 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Foggia (41,22 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 54&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 32&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 58&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 32&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 58&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 54&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 28&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordm; 54&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>41&ordm; 32&apos;</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PERIODI DI VIGENZA</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;decreto</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Inizio</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Anni</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>1&ordm;&nbsp;periodo</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>24/01/1975</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left>Conferimento</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>24/01/1975</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=center>24/01/2005</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=right>30</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top align=left></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>PROVVEDIMENTI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Natura&nbsp;del&nbsp;provvedimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Decorrenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Pubblicazione&nbsp;BUIG</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/01/1975</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/798_19750124.pdf" target=_blank>Conferimento</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/01/1975</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XIX N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/12/1978</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/798_19781212.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/12/1978</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXIII N. 2</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/09/1979</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/798_19790926.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">26/09/1979</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XXIII N. 11</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 