      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>NOVA SIRI SCALO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>751</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/05/1963</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>2&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">24/05/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>7,50 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>Presentata in data 18 maggio 2016 e pubblicata nel BUIG Anno LX - N. 5 istanza di rinuncia all&apos;istanza di proroga presentata in data 31 maggio 2011.<br>Nell'ambito della concessione non sono presenti impianti.<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">GAS PLUS ITALIANA</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>100%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>BASILICATA (7,5 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Matera (7,5 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 10&apos;,77</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 10&apos;,14</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 12&apos;,57</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 09&apos;,28</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 11&apos;,63</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 08&apos;,14</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 09&apos;,84</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>40&ordm; 09&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px soli