  <Placemark>
      <name>TORRENTE MENOCCHIA</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Concessione di Coltivazione</h3><h2>TORRENTE MENOCCHIA</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Codice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Conferimento</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Periodo&nbsp;di&nbsp;vigenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Scadenza</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>796</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/01/1974</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordf; proroga</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">20/01/2024</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>23,30 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr></table><u>Note</u><br>Presentata in data 21 settembre 2023 rinuncia all&apos;istanza di proroga del 20 gennaio 2022<br>Nell'ambito della concessione non sono presenti impianti.<br><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>TITOLARI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Operatore</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Quota</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">ENERGEAN ITALY(r.u.)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>88%</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">PETROREP ITALIANA S.R.L. IN LIQUIDAZIONE</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=right>12%</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>REGIONI E PROVINCE IN CUI IL TITOLO RICADE (superfici parziali)</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td valign=top>MARCHE (23,3 km<sup>2</sup>)</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Ascoli Piceno (23,3 km<sup>2</sup>)<br></td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI</div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 18&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 04&apos;,43</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 18&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 04&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 19&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 04&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>1&ordm; 19&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>43&ordm; 03&apos;</td></tr><tr><td