di esplorazione</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">02/04/1996</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XL N. 5</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">13/02/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1002_19980213.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/01/1998</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">12/02/2004</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1002_20040212.pdf" target=_blank>Intestazione quota</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/12/2003</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno XLVIII N. 3</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/08/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1002_20180801.pdf" target=_blank>Trasferimento quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">01/07/2018</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXII N. 7</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">19/03/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;"><a href="https://unmig.mase.gov.it/wp-content/uploads/decreti/1002_20210319.pdf" target=_blank>Cambio intestazione quote</a></td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">23/02/2021</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">Anno LXV N. 3</td></tr></table><br><div style=&apos;margin-bottom:5px;&apos;>IMPIANTI</div>]]></description>
